report_inst_space_group(25.10)                  report_inst_space_group(25.10)

Name
       report_inst_space_group  -  Reports  all instance space groups into the
       inst_space_group report file by default

Syntax
       report_inst_space_group

       [-help]

       [-file <fileName>]

       [-group <groupName>]

       Reports all instance space groups into the inst_space_group report file
       by default.

Parameters
       -file <fileName>
              Specifies the file name to dump space group

       -group< groupName>
              Specifies the name of the group to be reported.

       -help  Outputs a brief description that includes type and  default  in-
              formation for each report_inst_space_group parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command: man report_inst_space_group.

